

{%- if page.handle == 'care-guide' -%}
  {%- comment -%} ─── NauNau Care Guide ─── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="naunau-care">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="nc-hero">
      <p class="nc-hero-eyebrow nc-animate">NauNau Care Guide</p>
      <h1 class="nc-animate nc-delay-1">Love your bags,<br><em>and they'll love you back.</em></h1>
      <p class="nc-hero-sub nc-animate nc-delay-2">A little TLC goes a long way. Here's everything you need to keep your NauNau bags fresh, clean, and lasting for years — not landfills.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- QUICK WINS BAR -->
    <div class="nc-quick-wins">
      <div class="nc-quick-win"><span class="nc-icon">🍽️</span> Dishwasher safe</div>
      <div class="nc-quick-win"><span class="nc-icon">☀️</span> Self-cleaning in sunlight</div>
      <div class="nc-quick-win"><span class="nc-icon">♾️</span> Built to last forever</div>
      <div class="nc-quick-win"><span class="nc-icon">🌿</span> 100% food-grade silicone</div>
    </div>

    <div class="nc-container">

      <!-- WASHING -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">🧼</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">Everyday Care</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Washing your NauNau bags</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">Good news — cleaning your NauNau is genuinely easy. Two options, zero stress.</p>
        <div class="nc-callout nc-sage">
          <div class="nc-callout-icon">✅</div>
          <div class="nc-callout-body">
            <p class="nc-callout-title">Dishwasher? Go for it.</p>
            <p class="nc-callout-text">Chuck them on any rack — top or bottom, NauNau doesn't mind. Just skip the inside-out flip (more on that below).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nc-callout nc-cream">
          <div class="nc-callout-icon">🚿</div>
          <div class="nc-callout-body">
            <p class="nc-callout-title">Hand washing works great too.</p>
            <p class="nc-callout-text">Warm, soapy water + a bottle brush for the corners = squeaky clean. Done.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- INSIDE OUT WARNING -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">🙅</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">The Golden Rule</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Please don't flip them inside out</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">We know it's tempting — it looks just like a plastic bag. But resist! Here's why it matters:</p>
        <div class="nc-callout nc-terracotta">
          <div class="nc-callout-icon">⚠️</div>
          <div class="nc-callout-body">
            <p class="nc-callout-title">The edges are the secret sauce.</p>
            <p class="nc-callout-text">Your NauNau's sealed edges are bonded with pure platinum food-grade silicone, then cured for strength. Flipping inside out stresses those seams and can cause tears over time. Treat those edges like the precious things they are.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ODORS -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">🧅</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">Freshening Up</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Banishing stubborn smells</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">Silicone is naturally odour-resistant, but onions and garlic have a way of making themselves at home. Here's how to evict them:</p>
        <div class="nc-steps">
          <div class="nc-step">
            <div class="nc-step-num">1</div>
            <div class="nc-step-text"><strong>The vinegar soak.</strong> Mix equal parts warm water and white vinegar, then let your bag soak for a few hours. Simple, effective, and very satisfying.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="nc-step">
            <div class="nc-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="nc-step-text"><strong>The oven trick.</strong> Pop it on a baking sheet and bake for 8 minutes at 180°C (350°F). Use oven mitts — silicone holds heat! Let it cool completely before touching.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="nc-step">
            <div class="nc-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="nc-step-text"><strong>For serious offenders (looking at you, kimchi):</strong> Do both. Vinegar soak first, then a quick bake. Your bag will come out smelling like nothing at all — which is exactly the goal.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STAINS -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">☀️</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">Natural Magic</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Getting rid of stains</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">This one never gets old — sunlight is NauNau's best friend.</p>
        <div class="nc-callout nc-sage">
          <div class="nc-callout-icon">✨</div>
          <div class="nc-callout-body">
            <p class="nc-callout-title">Leave it in the sun for a few hours.</p>
            <p class="nc-callout-text">UV light naturally bleaches out stains — no harsh chemicals needed. Tomato sauce, carrot, watermelon, beetroot... sunlight handles them all. Just set your bag on the windowsill or outside and let nature do its thing. It genuinely works like magic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MOLD PREVENTION -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">🌿</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">Prevention is Everything</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Keeping mold away</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">Mold needs two things: food particles and moisture. Take those away and it has nowhere to go.</p>
        <ul class="nc-tips-list">
          <li>Rinse out food residue after every use — a quick rinse is all it takes.</li>
          <li>A bottle brush is brilliant for getting into the corners properly.</li>
          <li>For extra peace of mind, give your bag a quick soak in white vinegar or a dip in boiling water. Either one sanitises beautifully.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- DRYING -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">💨</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">After the Wash</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Drying your bags properly</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">Silicone is a bit of a water collector — give it the time it needs to dry fully.</p>
        <ul class="nc-tips-list">
          <li>Stand bags upright over a bottle, cup, or paper towel holder so air can circulate inside. Works a treat.</li>
          <li>A drying rack (bamboo or otherwise) is your best friend here — bags can hang open and dry thoroughly.</li>
          <li>Air drying might leave harmless water spots. If that bothers you, just wipe down with a clean cloth before storing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- STORING -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">🗄️</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">Between Uses</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Storing your NauNau bags</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="nc-section-intro">A little thought about storage keeps your bags in perfect shape.</p>
        <ul class="nc-tips-list">
          <li>Always store bags with the seal <em>open</em> — this lets moisture escape and prevents any build-up inside.</li>
          <li>Flat in a drawer or stacked in a basket both work well. They're flexible, literally.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- DO / DON'T -->
      <div class="nc-section">
        <div class="nc-section-header">
          <div class="nc-section-emoji">📋</div>
          <div class="nc-section-title-wrap">
            <p class="nc-section-tag">The Quick Reference</p>
            <h2 class="nc-section-title">Do's &amp; don'ts at a glance</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nc-do-dont">
          <div class="nc-do-card">
            <p class="nc-card-label">✅ Do this</p>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Wash in the dishwasher or by hand</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Air dry fully before storing</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Use sunlight to remove stains</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Rinse after every single use</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Store with the seal open</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Open the seal gently, rolling down from each side</div>
          </div>
          <div class="nc-dont-card">
            <p class="nc-card-label">🚫 Skip this</p>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Flipping inside out (ever!)</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Storing sharp objects inside</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Using as a cutting board</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Forcing the seal open farther than natural</div>
            <div class="nc-card-item"><div class="nc-dot"></div>Storing while still damp</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /nc-container -->

    <!-- FOOTER CTA -->
    <div class="nc-footer-callout">
      <h2>Questions? We're here for it.</h2>
      <p>Looking after your NauNau bags means fewer trips to the bin and more space in your kitchen for things that actually matter.</p>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="nc-btn">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    /* ─── NauNau Care Guide — scoped to .naunau-care ─── */
    .naunau-care { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.6; }
    .naunau-care * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    /* Hero */
    .naunau-care .nc-hero { background-color: #1A1A1A; padding: 80px 40px 70px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .naunau-care .nc-hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(122,158,126,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(196,113,74,0.13) 0%, transparent 55%); }
    .naunau-care .nc-hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #B5CEB8; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; }
    .naunau-care .nc-hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem); font-weight: 700; color: #FFFDF9; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; }
    .naunau-care .nc-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #E8A882; }
    .naunau-care .nc-hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; color: #D9D4CC; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }

    /* Quick wins */
    .naunau-care .nc-quick-wins { background: #7A9E7E; padding: 20px 40px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .naunau-care .nc-quick-win { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: white; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
    .naunau-care .nc-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; }

    /* Container */
    .naunau-care .nc-container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

    /* Sections */
    .naunau-care .nc-section { padding: 56px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #D9D4CC; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section-header { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section-emoji { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7A9E7E; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.55rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; line-height: 1.2; }
    .naunau-care .nc-section-intro { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #6B6B6B; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* Callout boxes */
    .naunau-care .nc-callout { border-radius: 12px; padding: 22px 26px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .naunau-care .nc-sage { background-color: #E8F0E9; border-left: 3px solid #7A9E7E; }
    .naunau-care .nc-terracotta { background-color: #F9EDE6; border-left: 3px solid #C4714A; }
    .naunau-care .nc-cream { background-color: #F4EFE6; border-left: 3px solid #D9D4CC; }
    .naunau-care .nc-callout-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-callout-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-callout-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #6B6B6B; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* Steps */
    .naunau-care .nc-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-step { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 18px 20px; background: #FFFDF9; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #D9D4CC; }
    .naunau-care .nc-step-num { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: #C4714A; color: white; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .naunau-care .nc-step-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.6; padding-top: 3px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-step-text strong { color: #1A1A1A; }

    /* Tips list */
    .naunau-care .nc-tips-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-tips-list li { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.6; }
    .naunau-care .nc-tips-list li::before { content: '\2192'; color: #7A9E7E; font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* Do / Don't */
    .naunau-care .nc-do-dont { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-do-card, .naunau-care .nc-dont-card { border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-do-card { background: #E8F0E9; }
    .naunau-care .nc-dont-card { background: #F9EDE6; }
    .naunau-care .nc-card-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-do-card .nc-card-label { color: #7A9E7E; }
    .naunau-care .nc-dont-card .nc-card-label { color: #C4714A; }
    .naunau-care .nc-card-item { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.5; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-card-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .naunau-care .nc-dot { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 5px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .naunau-care .nc-do-card .nc-dot { background: #7A9E7E; }
    .naunau-care .nc-dont-card .nc-dot { background: #C4714A; }

    /* Footer CTA */
    .naunau-care .nc-footer-callout { background: #1A1A1A; padding: 56px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .naunau-care .nc-footer-callout h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #FFFDF9; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .naunau-care .nc-footer-callout p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #D9D4CC; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto 24px; font-weight: 300; }
    .naunau-care .nc-btn { display: inline-block; background: #C4714A; color: white; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .naunau-care .nc-btn:hover { background: #E8A882; }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes ncFadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .naunau-care .nc-animate { animation: ncFadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
    .naunau-care .nc-delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .naunau-care .nc-delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

    /* Mobile */
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .naunau-care .nc-do-dont { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .naunau-care .nc-quick-wins { gap: 20px; }
    }
  </style>

{%- else -%}

<div class="section-background color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}"></div>
<div class="section page-width-content color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <div
    class="
      spacing-style
      layout-panel-flex
      layout-panel-flex--column
      section-content-wrapper
      mobile-column
    "
    style="
      {% render 'layout-panel-style', settings: section.settings %}
      {% render 'spacing-style', settings: section.settings %}
    "
  >
    {% content_for 'blocks' %}
  </div>
</div>

{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "t:names.page",
  "class": "section-wrapper",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "@theme"
    },
    {
      "type": "@app"
    },
    {
      "type": "_divider"
    }
  ],
  "disabled_on": {
    "groups": ["header"]
  },
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "content_direction",
      "label": "t:settings.direction",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "column",
          "label": "t:options.vertical"
        }
      ],
      "default": "column",
      "visible_if": "{{ section.settings.gap < 0 }}"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "gap",
      "label": "t:settings.gap",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "t:settings.color_scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "t:content.padding"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-block-start",
      "label": "t:settings.top",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding-block-end",
      "label": "t:settings.bottom",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
